    "ayahNumber": 4,
    "arabicText": "يَوْمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلْفَرَاشِ ٱلْمَبْثُوثِ",
    "translationText": "The Day when the people will be like scattered moths."
  },
  {
    "surahId": 101,
    "ayahNumber": 5,
    "arabicText": "وَتَكُونُ ٱلْجِبَالُ كَٱلْعِهْنِ ٱلْمَنفُوشِ",
    "translationText": "And the mountains will be like tufted wool."
  },
  {
